content: Hi Julie! Our text trainings have ended, but you can check out ⁠⁠<#1268426751164551199> to look through or ask about other texting opportunities. You can also go to https://go.kamalaharris.com/ to find more ways to get involved. We would love help with making phone calls during this final stretch -- you can sign up for that at https://events.democrats.org/event/725393/ . Thank you!
